        <p class="text-sm text-amber-300 font-semibold mb-3">P=3, H=4, O=1, E=1, N=1, I=1, X=8 · 7 letters · Uses X tile</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">The mythical bird reborn from ashes. PHOENIX scores 19 points with X=8 doing the heavy lifting. As a 7-letter word, it qualifies for the 50-point bingo bonus — that's 69 total points if you play all your tiles.</p>
