        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10"><p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🦁 SPHINX</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">18 pts · S=1, P=3, H=4, I=1, N=1, X=8 · Riddle creature</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10"><p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🧚 NYMPH</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">15 pts · N=1, Y=4, M=3, P=3, H=4 · Nature spirit</p></div>
